text.tspan: Layers are provided to allow creation of PAX and cargo liveries in one SVG source. If
the liveries have common paint, place that in the Common Paint layer. Anything
specific to cargo goes into Cargo Paint and anything specific to PAX goes into PAX paint.
When exporting the bitmap (suggested 2048x2048), ensure that these layers are hidden:
For PAX liveries, hide the Cargo Paint and Cargo Fittings layers.
For cargo liveries, hide the PAX Paint and PAX Fittings layers.
Depending on the livery, also hide the BusStripe layer (default bus stripe).
All other layers should be visible (Common Paint, Shadows, Complete and Background).
For the best quality images and logos, repaint in your SVG editor rather than using bitmaps.
